"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the final, if you have a lane, you have a chance.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lane\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we were all fighting,\\\" an emotional Tatjana added.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an emotional Tatjana\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The emotions were really \\u2026 it took a village to get me where I am today.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The emotions\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"a village\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know they would have been proud, even if I did not get a medal, but it was really for them,\\\" Smith said.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was for everyone that has been with me, who believed in me and for my country as well.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our hashtag is 'for my country \\u2026' it really is, just to inspire someone at home and to know that they do not have to disqualify themselves and potentially be an Olympic champion,\\\" Tatjana further explained.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our hashtag\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\":